
public class GreatestNumber {

	public static void main(String[] args) {
		// TODO Auto-generated method stub
		

		 int x = 101;
		 int y = 89;
		 int z = 124;
	
		 if(x > y && x > z)
	     {
		    System.out.println(x);
		 }
		 else if(y > z)
	     {
		    System.out.println(y);
		 }
		 else
		 {
		    System.out.println(z);
		 }
		 
	}

}
